<exercise checkit-seed="0000" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
                <p> Blanca is gambling \$13 on rolling a 2 on a 4-sided die. If Blanca wins, they win \$31, otherwise they forfit their bet. What is the expected value of this gamble?
                </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <me>\frac{1}{4}(31) + \frac{3}{4}(-13) = -$2.0</me>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
